        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is ProWritingAid good for SEO writing?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "It improves readability and clarity, which indirectly helps SEO. But it has zero SEO features — no keyword research, no SERP analysis, no content scoring against ranking pages, no internal-link suggestions. For SEO content you pair it with Ahrefs or Surfer, or you use a tool like theStacc that handles writing and SEO together." }},
